snippet.title: Nanokin - IWOCon 2020 Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out more updates at https://twitter.com/studioanjin

Run, jump, slide and glide your way through this Cyberpunk RPG adventure!

Gain allies, build your own Nanokin and battle it out through the fantastical worlds of the Nanoverse!

Discover the secrets lurking underneath the charming theme park exterior in this unique hybrid of exploration platformer and strategic turn based combat. 

Will you unlock the secret of Nanokin?
